<Paragraph><Run FontWeight="Bold">Axis Elements Positioning and Grid Lines Customization</Run></Paragraph><Paragraph>ChartAxis GridLines appearance can be customized with individual properties available for each of the ChartAxis elements and the axis elments can be altered to some relative positions with respect to its default location.

</Paragraph><Paragraph TextAlignment="Center">
