<Paragraph  FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="16" TextAlignment="Center">
Fig: <Bold>ChartAxis Elements Configuration Demo</Bold>
</Paragraph>

<Paragraph FontWeight="Bold" FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="16">
Features
</Paragraph>

<List Margin="25,0,0,0">
<ListItem><Paragraph>Grid Lines,Tick Lines,Small Tick Lines of the chart axis can be customized.</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Orgin property of both primary axis and secondary axis can be customized.</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Axis properties like Visibility axis, Orientation can also be customized.</Paragraph></ListItem>
</List>

<Paragraph FontWeight="Bold" FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="16">
Interactive Features</Paragraph>
<List Margin="25,0,0,0">
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The colorpicker <Bold>"GridLineStroke"</Bold> helps to set the color for the Major GridLines in axis. </Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The colorpicker <Bold>"MinorGridLineStroke"</Bold> helps to set the color for the Minor GridLines in axis. </Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The colorpicker <Bold>"SmallTickStroke"</Bold> helps to set the color for the SmallTickLines in axis. </Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The colorpicker <Bold>"SmallTickStroke"</Bold> helps to set the color for the TickLines in axis. </Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The text box <Bold>"Origin"</Bold> helps to set the Origin for the Chart PrimaryAxis. </Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The Checkbox <Bold>"IsOriginCentred"</Bold> helps to set the Origin on the PrimaryAxis.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
 <ListItem>
<Paragraph>The combo box <Bold>"Axis Visibility"</Bold> helps to set the visibility of PrimaryAxis.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
 <ListItem>
<Paragraph>The above properties can also be applied to Chart SecondaryAxis in the same way.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
</List>
</FlowDocument>